headers.subject: [tosdr:2594] Stack Exchange notifies you of pricing changes

html:
Stack Exchange may change its prices at any time but will provide you reasonable notice of any such changes by posting the new prices on the Network and by sending you email notification. If you do not wish to pay the new prices, you may cancel the services prior to the change going into effect.

http://stackexchange.com/legal

Title: Stack Exchange notifies you of pricing changes

Topic: user-info

Summary: Stack Exchange provides certain paid services. They may change the prices of these services at any time, but they will notify you by email. This allows you the opportunity to cancel the service before the pricing change happens.

Score: 40 (good)
